  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this third person multiplayer soccer game, compete in matches at different maps from 2v2 up to 5v5, create private matches and invite friends, chat with players, and increase your stats with scoring goals, assists or other performable! There is no goalkeeper but a strong muscle protecting it, so time your shot!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat content doesn't break the core soccer gameplay neither shooting abilities makes it easy to goal, it's still based on player skills! Could be played without using any of available ones!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playing with team is one of the most important, even a player can goal from gate to gate but it's not as strategic as using right skills in time and coordinating with your team!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No major game bugs! Well tested and prepared for players!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your ultimate shooting skills and make coolish moves to take the ball to the goal!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/118f868de58c1a85505d3bf6929dbf4e.poster.avif?t=1741597953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/118f868de58c1a85505d3bf6929dbf4e.webm?t=1741597953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/118f868de58c1a85505d3bf6929dbf4e.mp4?t=1741597953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your ultimate attacking and dodging skills to combat or tackle the enemy!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/0ffc16f3e8abe6893909b87c26b45ffc.poster.avif?t=1741597953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/0ffc16f3e8abe6893909b87c26b45ffc.webm?t=1741597953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/0ffc16f3e8abe6893909b87c26b45ffc.mp4?t=1741597953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And use your kicking skills to perform best shots in the match, be in cooperation with your team, and rush to the win! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/e853891e138a3d75273aac6fda58fa54.poster.avif?t=1741597953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/e853891e138a3d75273aac6fda58fa54.webm?t=1741597953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/e853891e138a3d75273aac6fda58fa54.mp4?t=1741597953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More maps and skills also new gameplay updates will come after release!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this third person multiplayer soccer game, compete in matches at different maps from 2v2 up to 5v5, create private matches and invite friends, chat with players, and increase your stats with scoring goals, assists or other performable! There is no goalkeeper but a strong muscle protecting it, so time your shot!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat content doesn't break the core soccer gameplay neither shooting abilities makes it easy to goal, it's still based on player skills! Could be played without using any of available ones!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playing with team is one of the most important, even a player can goal from gate to gate but it's not as strategic as using right skills in time and coordinating with your team!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No major game bugs! Well tested and prepared for players!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your ultimate shooting skills and make coolish moves to take the ball to the goal!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/118f868de58c1a85505d3bf6929dbf4e.poster.avif?t=1741597953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/118f868de58c1a85505d3bf6929dbf4e.webm?t=1741597953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/118f868de58c1a85505d3bf6929dbf4e.mp4?t=1741597953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your ultimate attacking and dodging skills to combat or tackle the enemy!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/0ffc16f3e8abe6893909b87c26b45ffc.poster.avif?t=1741597953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/0ffc16f3e8abe6893909b87c26b45ffc.webm?t=1741597953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/0ffc16f3e8abe6893909b87c26b45ffc.mp4?t=1741597953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And use your kicking skills to perform best shots in the match, be in cooperation with your team, and rush to the win! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/e853891e138a3d75273aac6fda58fa54.poster.avif?t=1741597953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/e853891e138a3d75273aac6fda58fa54.webm?t=1741597953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413330/extras/e853891e138a3d75273aac6fda58fa54.mp4?t=1741597953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More maps and skills also new gameplay updates will come after release!</p></li></ul>",
